latestPosts.caption:
Pramukh Varni Din | Jeth Sud 4

Today we commemorate the sacred day when Pramukh Swami Maharaj, the creator of Swaminarayan Akshardham, New Delhi, was appointed as President (Pramukh) of @BAPS Swaminarayan Sanstha by his Guru, Shastriji Maharaj, the founder of BAPS.

Exactly 75 years ago, at just 28, Shastri Narayanswarupdasji humbly accepted this lifelong responsibility — marking the beginning of a spiritual legacy rooted in humility, seva, and universal love.

His life and leadership continue to uplift and inspire millions worldwide. 🕊️

#PramukhVarniDin #PramukhSwamiMaharaj #PramukhSwami
#BAPS #Swaminarayan #Akshardham #DelhiAkshardham
latestPosts.alt: An artistic illustration depicting the historic moment when Shastriji Maharaj appointed Pramukh Swami Maharaj as President of BAPS Swaminarayan Sanstha. Shastriji Maharaj is shown placing a shawl on young Shastri Narayanswarupdas (later Pramukh Swami Maharaj) in a traditional ceremony, while Yogiji Maharaj respectfully witnesses and blesses the occasion.

latestPosts.caption:
Discover the first traditional Hindu mandir in Paris where Indian craftsmanship meets French ingenuity 🇮🇳🇫🇷

A sacred space for peace, reflection and devotion is rising in the heart of France, a dream nurtured for over 50 years, now coming to life through the unwavering dedication and spiritual guidance of His Holiness Mahant Swami Maharaj.

Visit the link in @bapsparis bio to watch the full video.

Today (Vaishak Vad 12), on the 133rd birth anniversary of His Holiness Yogiji Maharaj, the fourth spiritual successor of Bhagwan Swaminarayan, we reflect on his timeless wisdom, unwavering service to humanity, and deep faith in future generations.

His life continues to inspire us to stay rooted in our values and traditions—no matter where in the world we may be.

#YogijiMaharaj #BAPS #Akshardham

Blackout Mock Drill at #Akshardham

Emergency Preparedness Drill at Akshardham

Today, Swaminarayan Akshardham, New Delhi, conducted a comprehensive mock drill – Operation Sindoor – in collaboration with Delhi Police and emergency response teams.

The exercise aimed to assess and enhance on-ground coordination, response time, and preparedness for potential emergency situations.

We remain committed to the safety and security of all visitors and devotees.

#OperationSindoor #MockDrill #EmergencyPreparedness #DelhiPolice
#AkshardhamDelhi #SafetyFirst

Moments from the U.S. Vice President JD Vance, Second Lady Usha Vance & their children visit to Swaminarayan Akshardham in Delhi—their first stop in India—experiencing its majestic art, architecture & timeless values of faith, family & harmony.

#IndiaUSrelations #jdvance #usindiadosti
@vp @jdvance @slotus 
#BAPS #Akshardham

-------

Vice President of the United States Visits Swaminarayan Akshardham, New Delhi

New Delhi, 21 April 2025 – The Vice President of the United States, JD Vance, along with his wife, Second Lady Usha Vance, and their children—Ewan, Vivek, and Mirabel—visited Swaminarayan Akshardham in New Delhi as the first stop of his maiden official visit to India.

The Vance family explored the mandir’s majestic art and architecture, experiencing India’s heritage and cultural depth. They appreciated the messages of harmony, family values, and timeless wisdom embodied in the Akshardham campus.

Vice President Vance was presented a personal letter of blessings and prayers from His Holiness Mahant Swami Maharaj. The letter expressed heartfelt gratitude for the visit and special prayers for the well-being of the Vice President and his family, as well as for the continued unity and progress of the United States of America.

As a gesture of friendship, the Vance family was presented with several commemorative gifts, including a model of the Swaminarayan Akshardham mandir, intricately carved wooden elephants, literature about the Swaminarayan Akshardham campuses in New Delhi and Robbinsville (USA), and value-based illustrated storybooks for their children. A framed family photograph taken in front of the mandir was also presented as a special memento.

The visit symbolizes the shared values of faith, peace, and unity that continue to strengthen ties between India and the United States.

Sharing his experience in the guest book, US Vice President JD Vance  wrote:

“Thank you all so much for your hospitality and kindness in welcoming me and my family to this beautiful place. It is a great credit to India that you built a beautiful temple with precision and care. Our kids, in particular, loved it. God bless.”

latestPosts.caption:
Prayers for Pahalgam

BAPS condemns the brutal terrorist attack in Pahalgam, Jammu & Kashmir, India.

His Holiness Mahant Swami Maharaj and BAPS worldwide continue to pray for the innocent victims and their families, and for the recovery of the injured. 

We also pray that in this hour of deep grief and shock, may the whole world unite to take conscious and collective action to uproot terrorism everywhere and anywhere in the world.

परमार्थम हनुमान मंदिर में आज का दिन अत्यंत शुभ और दिव्य रहा, जब हमारे बीच पधारे पूज्य संत— पूज्य भद्रेश दास स्वामी जी , स्वामी श्री मुनिवत्सल दास जी महाराज एवं श्री धरम मूर्ति जी महाराज, जो कि दिल्ली अक्षरधाम मंदिर से पधारे हैं, साथ ही स्वामी श्री कंचन गिरि जी महाराज, महामंडलेश्वर श्री नवल किशोर दास जी (महामंत्री, दिल्ली संत महामंडल) एवं महंत श्री धीरेंद्र पुरी जी महाराज। इन सभी महापुरुषों की पावन उपस्थिति ने मंदिर परिसर को आध्यात्मिक ऊर्जा, सकारात्मकता और दिव्यता से आलोकित कर दिया। उनका सान्निध्य हमारे लिए सौभाग्य और प्रेरणा का स्रोत बना। परमार्थम परिवार की ओर से हम इन महान संतों का हृदयपूर्वक स्वागत और आभार व्यक्त करते हैं।

✨ Shri Ram Janmotsav ✨
On this auspicious day of Chaitra Sud 9, we celebrate the birth of Bhagwan Shri Ram—an embodiment of dharma, resilience, and unwavering devotion. His ideals of truth, duty, and selfless love continue to guide and inspire millions.

May Bhagwan Ram’s divine virtues lead us towards righteousness and inner strength. Let us imbibe his teachings and strive to become the best version of ourselves.

Jay Shri Ram!
